  "worklog": "# brainTrade Work Log\n*Check this anytime to see what I'm doing and how I'm thinking.*\n\n---\n## 2026-03-31 14:42 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 2] Triple-Logging Bug RESOLVED + V5a Readiness Check\n\n**Task:** Investigate async triple-logging bug and assess V5a deployment readiness.\n\n**Triple-Logging Bug \u2014 RESOLVED:**\n- Was NOT an async/code bug \u2014 it was orphan processes from zombie bash parents\n- After zombie parents killed (P4 work), watchdog cleaned orphans at 13:55\n- Log now shows single sequential counter: 300\u2192360\u2192420 (exactly 10min intervals)\n- Confirmed: ONE process, ONE loop, ONE counter. Bug closed.\n\n**V5a Deployment Readiness (target: Apr 6):**\n| Check | Status |\n|-------|--------|\n| min_bias=45 backtest | \u2705 78 trades, 59.0% WR vs 51.2% (+7.8pp) |\n| Patch ready | \u2705 `patches/v5a-min-bias-45.patch.md` |\n| Process stability | \u2705 Single process, clean watchdog |\n| Indicator logging | \u23f3 Need 1 trade with clean single-process |\n| 5 stable days | \u23f3 Need Apr 1-5 |\n\n**V5a impact projection:**\n- 52% fewer trades but each +7.8pp higher WR\n- Cuts the 51.2% WR \"coin flip\" trades (bias 25-45)\n- Keeps the 59.0% WR \"real signal\" trades (bias \u226545)\n- Volume drops from ~8/day to ~4/day but profit per trade increases\n\n**Today's single trade:** bias=-58.4 (KEEP under V5a), won=True. No indicators in JSONL (trade was from zombie process). Next trade at 19h will be the definitive indicator test.\n\n**Next P2:** After 19h trade, verify indicator logging works. If confirmed, all V5a blockers except time-based stability are cleared.\n\n---\n## 2026-03-31 14:16 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 1] Copy Intelligence: Daily Threshold Markets = Human Trading Opportunity\n\n**Task:** Investigate PM daily/weekly markets for human copy trading (5-min markets are 100% bots).\n\n**Finding \u2014 PM Market Structure:**\n- 165 active 5-min Up/Down markets (our current arena \u2014 100% bots)\n- 19 daily threshold markets (\"BTC